---
title: Fresh Shrimp Salad Endive Bites Serves 6 | with Cucumber and Guacamole
description: Guests will be wowed by this stunner of an opener featuring shrimp in zippy, creamy dressing and served on crisp endive leaves. What they won't know? How easy it was!

The ingredients and nutritional values listed below are based on 6 servings.

Ingredients: Belgian endive • Shrimp • Limes • Cucumber • Guacamole (hass avocado, tomato, onion, sea salt, garlic, cilantro, cilantro essential oil) • Mayonnaise  (canola and/or soy oil, liquid whole egg, frozen egg yolk, water, salt, sugar, vinegar, concentrated lemon juice, spice extract, mustard, lactic acid, calcium disodium EDTA) (mustard, egg) • Chives.
